OL,6,FThe family of a runner killed by a low-
OL,7,Fhanging electricity cable has issued a
OL,8,Fstatement, following the conclusion of
OL,9,Fan inquest into his death.
OL,11,F29-year-old John Henry Oates, known as
OL,12,FHarry, was found dead near Kendal on
OL,13,FOctober 27, 2023.
OL,15,FAn inquest concluded that a "rare and
OL,16,Fcomplex sequence of events" led to his
OL,17,Fdeath, after he came into contact with
OL,18,Fan electricity cable.
