OL,6,FMr Oates' family has now said it
OL,7,Fbelieves "this was not a random or
OL,8,Funique accident".
OL,10,FIn a statement, they said: "There were
OL,11,Fmissed opportunities to prevent what
OL,12,Fhappened, and similar incidents have
OL,13,Foccurred before. The wider risks were
OL,14,Fnot addressed, and there was a
OL,15,Freluctance to acknowledge this.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
