OL,4,Ccable make statement
OL,6,FThe family expressed its gratitude
OL,7,Fthat the Coroner issued a "Prevention
OL,8,Fof Future Deaths report", and hoped
OL,9,Fthat this "will prompt urgent action
OL,10,Fand meaningful change across the
OL,11,Findustry nationwide."
OL,13,FThe family expressed disappointment
OL,14,Fwith the Health and Safety Executive
OL,15,Fwho, they say, "failed" to investigate
OL,16,Fthe causes of insulator failure in a
OL,17,F2012 inquest, where in similar
OL,18,Fcircumstances Dr James Kew was killed
OL,19,Fwhen he came into contact with a low-
OL,20,Fhanging electricity cable while
OL,21,Frunning.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
