OL,3,CFamily of runner killed by electricity
OL,4,Ccable make statement
OL,6,FThe family's statement said: "Had the
OL,7,Finsulators been properly investigated
OL,8,Fat that time or after subsequent
OL,9,Ffailures, the underlying defects could
OL,10,Fhave been discovered."
OL,12,FThe family asked "for a thorough
OL,13,Freview of current practices, a
OL,14,Fcommitment to transparency, and a
OL,15,Frenewed focus on safety - so that our
OL,16,Fson's life is not lost in vain."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
